          },
          "description": "<ul><li>Project lead of client’s healthcare modelling initiative.</li><li>Designed and maintained two iterations of an end-to-end modelling tool: the first AWS-native leveraging SageMaker and Athena; the second on Snowflake with an H2O.ai backend coordinated by an internally developed Python API client.</li><li>Contributed to GAP’s AI and cloud strategy, published articles on GenAI ethics, and delivered talks on responsible ML development.</li></ul>",
          "roles": []
        },
